title: It's, plane, no it's a bullet... No, it's Super Speed Sion Jungle

embed.description: Welcome to my full play of super speed Sion jungle... So I hedged and went glass cannon and stack a phantom dancer, rapid fire cannon, shiv, boots of speed and blade of the ruined king to see what happens. End result, 18 kills!!! and a lot of lols. haha. BLOOD.

body: Check out m new video, didn't know what would happen if I stacks straight up beast levels of speed on him.  (he turns into king leonidas by endgame hahaha)
